question:
How many rectangles are in the array below?

[asy]
for(int i = 0; i<3; ++i)
{

for(int j = 0; j<3; ++j)

{

draw((3i,j)--(3i+3,j)--(3i+3,j+1)--(3i,j+1)--(3i,j)--cycle,linewidth(2));

}
}
[/asy]

The function $f(x)$ is graphed below.  Each small box has width and height 1.

[asy]
size(150);
import TrigMacros;
rr_cartesian_axes(-1,10,-1,10);

dot((1,7),red+5bp);
dot((2,4),red+5bp);
dot((3,1),red+5bp);
dot((4,8),red+5bp);
dot((5,5),red+5bp);
dot((6,2),red+5bp);
dot((7,9),red+5bp);
dot((8,6),red+5bp);
dot((9,3),red+5bp);
